project_core.project_title: Glioblastoma_200_cells_scale_test: Single-Cell RNAseq analysis of diffuse neoplastic infiltrating cells at the migrating front of human glioblastoma
project_core.project_description: Glioblastoma_200_cells_scale_test: We used single-cell RNAseq to investigate the heterogeneity of glioblastoma tumors and assess differential expression between cells within and in proximity of the tumor.
